&gt; On Fri, Oct 10, 2025 at 8:48 AM Stephen Chenney &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="196a7a717c77373737597a716b7674706c7437766b7e"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
