&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/gpuweb/gpuweb/blob/main/proposals/texture-component-swizzle.md"&gt;https://github.com/gpuweb/gpuweb/blob/main/proposals/texture-component-swizzle.md&lt;/a&gt;
*Specification*
&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://gpuweb.github.io/gpuweb/#dom-gpufeaturename-texture-component-swizzle"&gt;https://gpuweb.github.io/gpuweb/#dom-gpufeaturename-texture-component-swizzle&lt;/a&gt;
*Summary* Functionality added to the WebGPU spec after its first shipment in a browser.
Allows GPUTextureViews to rearrange or replace the color components from texture's red/green/blue/alpha channels when accessed by a shader.
*Blink component* Blink&gt;WebGPU
&lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3EWebGPU%22"&gt;https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3EWebGPU%22&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
