*TAG review* None
*TAG review status* Pending
*Risks*
*Interoperability and Compatibility* This feature has not yet been implemented yet in any browser. It has been approved by the GPU for the Web Community Group, with representatives from Chrome, Firefox, and Safari. See minutes at
&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/gpuweb/gpuweb/wiki/GPU-Web-2025%E2%80%9010-08#should-texture-swizzle-move-usage-restrictions-from-createview-to-createbindgroupbeginrenderpass-5298"&gt;https://github.com/gpuweb/gpuweb/wiki/GPU-Web-2025%E2%80%9010-08#should-texture-swizzle-move-usage-restrictions-from-createview-to-createbindgroupbeginrenderpass-5298&lt;/a&gt;,
&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/gpuweb/gpuweb/wiki/GPU-Web-2025%E2%80%9010-01#should-texture-swizzle-move-usage-restrictions-from-createview-to-createbindgroupbeginrenderpass-5298"&gt;https://github.com/gpuweb/gpuweb/wiki/GPU-Web-2025%E2%80%9010-01#should-texture-swizzle-move-usage-restrictions-from-createview-to-createbindgroupbeginrenderpass-5298&lt;/a&gt;, and
