&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20251008" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 08 Oct 2025 07:08:27 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
